<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad Truchseß von Pommersfelden, Landrichter zu Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Anweisung des Vogts zu Reicheneck, Diener des Adressaten, zur Freilassung des F. Kötreich von Waizenfeld, Armmann des Konrad Peminger, Kaplan der Frauenkirche zu Nürnberg, und verweist auf den Rechtsweg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_255" id="126v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_255_r2l9"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Truchſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>pomerfeld<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l10">Lantrichter cʒu Nuremberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_255_r2l11"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Conrad vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> her Conrad Pemẏnger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l12">Caplan hie in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawn Capellen cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> . vvie daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l13">ewr diener . der voyt cʒu Reychneck ſeinen Armman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l14"><expan cert="unknown">F</expan> . kötreych von <expan>vvecʒenfeld<ex>en</ex></expan> gefangen hab . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l15">mit <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> dıener ſchıcken wöllet / daʒ Er <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l16">Armman ledig laſʒ . das wöllen etc Vnd het dann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l17"><expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ~ ewr diener cʒu Jm icht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l18">vvil Jm der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> her <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> <expan>Pemyng<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l19"><expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> Armman <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> ſleunigs <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l20"><expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> Er des ermandt wirdt / vnd biten des ewr <expan>gütl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r2l21"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wıder bey dem poten <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_255" id="126v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Truchsess<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Pomerfeld<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        lantrichter czu Nuremberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Conrad, uns hat
                            <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> her Conrad Pemynger, caplan hie in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawn capellen czu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wie daz ewr diener, der voyt czu
                        Reychneck, seinen armman <expan cert="unknown">F.</expan> Kötreych von
                                <expan>Weczenfeld<ex>en</ex></expan> gefangen hab.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir mit
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> diener schicken wöllet, daz er
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> armman ledig lasz, das wöllen etc.
                        Und het dann <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> ewr diener czu im icht
                                <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darümb wil im der
                                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> her <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan>
<expan>Pemyng<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> armman
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> sleunigs
                                <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er des ermandt
                        wirdt; und biten des ewr <expan>gütl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider bey dem poten.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
